creator: Artinsoft GmbH - Artingame
descriptionHtml:
Watch out for your opponent's attack.

The main features of the game include:
● Enemies appear in various places, in the wilderness, in space, and on spaceships.
● Various weapons can be acquired and changed, such as swords, axes, spears, and great swords.
descriptionShort: Draw your sword's trajectory, cut your enemy!

descriptionHtml:
Hyper Saber is an exhilarating action-packed game that will leave you on the edge of your seat. So grab your saber and get ready to embark on an epic journey!
action-packed, thrilling, challenging, enemies, saber, graphics, immersive, excitement.
The main features of the game include:
● Enemies appear in various places, in the wilderness, in space, and on spaceships.
● Various Swords can be acquired and changed, such as Swords, Axes, Spears, and great Swords.
Come and joy with Star of Swords !!
